---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Stakeholders">
    <section class="space-y-12">
        <header class="max-w-4xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-600 mb-3">
                Planning
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Stakeholders
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
                The project affects a wide range of stakeholders. Below is a power‑interest matrix that
                groups each party based on their influence and interest in the outcome.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Stakeholder List</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">All identified stakeholders:</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Employees</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Customers</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Organization</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Drug-dealers</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Government</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Citizens</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Investors</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Technical suppliers</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Vandals</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">The unemployed</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Plumbers</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Tourists</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Teenagers</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Policemen</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Courts</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Human Rights organisations</span>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700">Project team</span>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-200 bg-indigo-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Matrix Explanation</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-700">
                    The matrix groups stakeholders by <strong>Power</strong> (ability to influence outcomes)
                    and <strong>Interest</strong> (level of concern about the project). This helps prioritize
                    engagement and communication strategies.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>

        <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Power–Interest Matrix</h2>

            <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 mb-2">Low Power • Low Interest</p>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Monitor</h3>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Employees</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Technical suppliers</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Plumbers</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Teenagers</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 mb-2">High Power • Low Interest</p>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Keep Satisfied</h3>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Government</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Courts</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Policemen</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 mb-2">Low Power • High Interest</p>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Keep Informed</h3>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Near residents (citizens)</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Drug-dealers</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">The unemployed</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Tourists</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Human Rights organisations</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
                    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 mb-2">High Power • High Interest</p>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Manage Closely</h3>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Customers</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Organization</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Investors</span>
                        <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 border border-slate-200">Vandals</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
</MainLayout>